episodes.title: Most People Are Using AI Wrong; Here's How to Deploy It Like a Super User
episodes.guest: Allie K. Miller — TIME's 100 Most Influential People in AI
episodes.description: In the debut episode of Generation AI, Allie K. Miller breaks down why most people are barely scratching the surface of what AI can do and shares the tactics that separate casual users from power users deploying it across their businesses and careers.
